Pick up the egg from the table
turn left and then walk towards the refrigerator
put the egg in the refrigerator for some time and then take the egg out of the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk forward to the sink, then turn left and walk to the white table across the room.
Pick up the egg on the edge of the table beneath the spatula.
Turn to the left and walk to the chair on the right, then turn to the left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the egg on a shelf next to the tomato, then close the fridge door for five seconds then take the egg out.
Turn to the left and walk across the room, and then turn right and walk to the table.
Place the egg on the table to the left of the bread.
Turn around to the left and walk over to the table.
Pick up the egg from the table.
Turn to the left and walk over to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the egg inside, close the door, open the door, and remove the egg.
Turn to the left and walk to the black table.
Place the egg on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Placing a cool egg on a table.
